    "description": {
      "value": "<p>When escaping tight spots, you defy the odds.<br><strong>Prerequisites</strong>: Any racial trait or feat that grants a d20 reroll, character level 5th.</p>\n<hr>\n<p><span id=\"ctl00_MainContent_DataListTypes_ctl00_LabelName\"><strong>Benefit</strong>: When you use an ability to reroll one d20 roll, you can spend 1 Resolve Point to reroll twice and use the highest of all three results. Once you use this ability, you can do so again only after a 10-minute rest to regain Stamina Points.</span></p>",
